### Working with Multiple Files

    site.scss, site.sass
    site.css.scss, site.css.sass

Store in a `./lib` Sub-directory of the Sass files

Start files to be imported with and underscore e.g. _nav.scss

    @import "lib/nav";
    @import "nav";

### Mixins

    @mixin wrap($wrap-width) {
      margin: 0 auto;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: left;
      max-width: $wrap-width;
    }
    
    #wrapper {
      @include wrap(960px);
    }

### Selector Inheritance

