### Functions

    $$base-font-size: 12 !default;
    
    @function pxs2ems($px: 0, $context: $base-font-size) {
      $ems: ($px / $context) * 1em;
      @return $ems;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: pxs2ems(24, 12);
    }

* Supports Various Math operations
* Converts Between Units automatically whenever it's possible

